---

<footer class="w-full bg-[#143D73] text-[#DEA921] py-10 md:py-14 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between gap-8 md:gap-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:gap-5">
      <div class="font-logo leading-tight">
        <img src="/assets/beranda/logo_footer.webp" alt="Tambak Bayan logo" class="h-10 sm:h-12 md:h-14 object-contain" />
        <span class="sr-only">Tambak Bayan GO-WEB</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/institutsenitambakbayan/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="w-11 h-11 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#DEA921]/10 hover:bg-[#DEA921]/20 transition-colors"
          aria-label="Instagram">
          <i class="fab fa-instagram text-lg"></i>
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:contact@tambakbayan.com"
          class="w-11 h-11 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#DEA921]/10 hover:bg-[#DEA921]/20 transition-colors"
          aria-label="Email">
          <i class="fas fa-envelope text-lg"></i>
        </a>
        <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/mW5gzKq7QU7jjZYP8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="w-11 h-11 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#DEA921]/10 hover:bg-[#DEA921]/20 transition-colors"
          aria-label="Lokasi">
          <i class="fas fa-location-dot text-lg"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <blockquote class="md:max-w-[55%] lg:max-w-[50%] font-sans">
      <p class="text-[#DEA921]/95 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
        "Semua proses akan menemukan keindahannya pada waktu yang tepat.
        Selama mural tetap hidup di dinding dan warga terus membuka meja
        bagi para tamu, Tambak Bayan akan terus bersuara"
        <cite class="block mt-2 font-semibold not-italic text-[#CF2A2A]">— Suseno Karja</cite>
      </p>
    </blockquote>
  </div>
</footer>
